  "title": "fix(refinementList): cap `maxFacetHits` to 100 for SFFV",
  "body": "We cap the [`maxFacetHits`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/api-parameters/maxFacetHits/) value to 100 because the Algolia API doesn't support a greater number.\r\n\r\nAn Enterprise customer has faced this issue in Vue InstantSearch and it's challenging to fix user-land.\r\n\r\nCloses #4521.",
